I agree with most of these suggestions.  There are a few i would changes / alterations, though.  They are as follows...<P><BR>"Summon Mana Shard lvl 44- Summons a No Drop mana shard, effect: Harvest. Casting time 4 seconds. Casting time when clicked for effect, 10 seconds. Mana Cost 10. Recast time 10 minutes. Mana gained 171-301."<P>I would take this out because they cant code recast times into items, thats why many items have such long casting times.<P><BR>Summon Mask of the Magician lvl 24- Summon No Rent Mask AC 1 Face or main slot, with random Racial Illusion.<P>This would never work.  It would be WAY too powerful, and the enchanters would b*tch way too much.  Perhaps instead you could summon a mask with a charge of a randome *elemental* illusion (that is something I have always wanted, personaly)<P><BR>Revitalize Summoning lvl 49- Heal over time to pet 600 hp.<P>I would either make this an instant heal, or a 900 point HoT.  Pets at 49 have about 2500 hp, so 600 isn't that big of a chunk.<P><BR>Revitalize Summoning lvl 57- an 800 hit point heal over time to pet.<P>I would make this ~1200 hp HoT for the same mana as the 49 one.  Takes 30 seconds (5 ticks)<P><BR>Summon Fires of Solusek Ro lvl 59- Summons a No Rent, No Drop fire crystal effect Manaskin. Mana cost 400. casting time when cast and clicked for effect 5 seconds. Max duration 2 hours.Spell Component 1 peridot. Self Protective skin 400. Self Mana regen (1).<P>Nah, not needed, in my opinion.  But nice idea  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P><BR>Strength of Brell Serillis lvl 60- 1000 heal over time to pet.<P>Should be a complete heal or complete heal over time, if you ask me.<P><BR>Everything else, i am liking  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">  Here are some opinions of my own...<P><BR>Warmth of the Sun - level 24; Illusion: Fire Elemental, mana regeneration (2), fire resist (10-20); reagent: malachite; casting cost: 150. Duration: 18 minutes.<P>Soothing Touch of Water - level 34; Illusion: Water Elemental, mana regeneration (2), hp regeneration (2); reagent: Malachite; casting cost: 150.  Duration: 18 minutes.<P>Toughness of Earth - level 44; Illusion: Earth Elemental, 10 sta, 100-150 hp buff; casting cost: 150; reagent: malachite.  Duration: 18 minutes.<P>Strength of the Wind - level 54; Illusion: Air Elemental, 20% speed increase, 30 ac; Casting cost: 200; reagent: malachite.  Duration: 18 minutes.<P>Power of the Elements - level 60; Illusion: Bugged Elemental (you know, the one enchanters are somtimes), 40 pt dmg shield, mana regen (6), 50 ac, 200 hp, levitate, 20% speed increase, fire / cold resist +40; mana cost: 500; reagent: peridot.  Duration: 72 minutes.<P><BR>Those are some spells i just made up.  Prolly got a little out of hand, but you get the main idea, right?  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0">  Love the ideas.  Keep them coming  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>Magnia, 54th Elementalist &lt;Ethos&gt;<BR>Brell Serilis
